未有辦法取得簽證，因此今日未能起行，陳同佳也十分無奈，盼望潘母能明白和理解。而律師團隊也曾約七次致電「單一窗口」，希望解決簽證問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%AE%A1%E6%B5%A9%E9%B3%B4-%E5%9B%A0%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E5%8F%96%E7%B0%BD%E8%AD%89%E4%BB%8A%E6%9C%AA%E8%83%BD%E8%B5%B4%E5%8F%B0-%E9%99%B3%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%B3%E4%BA%A6%E7%84%A1%E5%A5%88-020933087.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%25B5%25A9%25E9%25B3%25B4-%25E5%259B%25A0%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%258F%2596%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E8%25AD%2589%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%259C%25AA%25E8%2583%25BD%25E8%25B5%25B4%25E5%258F%25B0-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25BD%25B3%25E4%25BA%25A6%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25A5%2588-020933087.html&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRICLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=5878200c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%AE%A1%E6%B5%A9%E9%B3%B4-%E5%9B%A0%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E5%8F%96%E7%B0%BD%E8%AD%89%E4%BB%8A%E6%9C%AA%E8%83%BD%E8%B5%B4%E5%8F%B0-%E9%99%B3%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%B3%E4%BA%A6%E7%84%A1%E5%A5%88-020933087.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T04:47:10.000Z","msg":"屌你老母潘太仲話難以估計<br />\n用下個西腦分析下都知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a113286987a4ecda2f7325f7972da756d988e9","tid":2254634,"uid":291199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T04:47:17.000Z","msg":"旅遊簽證？<br />\n殺人犯喎啊神父"},{"pid":"79c516b30758a700acf01de9e9f645b5f8728528","tid":2254634,"uid":121076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T04:49:21.000Z","msg":"聖公會班主教神父點解會覺得自己會上到天堂<br />\n因信稱義? 你信刁大大同人民幣多過信耶穌囉"},{"pid":"5fe06cdd9d7215fa687a71cfe4a082bdcbf0e902","tid":2254634,"uid":282319,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"69faa0b3a2a9aa249a3fdd19ebbd047bac6b9d77","tid":2254634,"uid":89382,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"a99c926055933a954a2480d1a43430d47fe6f82e","tid":2254634,"uid":11291,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T03:48:44.000Z","msg":"佳仔不知幾爽"},"citedBy"